+}
+lines.push("");
+lines.push(
+  "Overall, the cohort contains multiple strong treatment-biomarker-style signals despite opaque feature labels: several binary features show large positive or negative response-rate differences, these signals remain after adjustment, and pairwise interaction scans identify clinically meaningful response heterogeneity where joint feature status departs from additivity. Null-control features with adequate prevalence showed no evidence of association, supporting that the strongest findings are not merely artifacts of sample size.",
+);
+
+fs.writeFileSync("analysis_summary.txt", `${lines.join("\n")}\n`);
